    {
      "id": "ex-li-1",
      "type": "listen",
      "skill": "listening",
      "prompt": "Listen to the food critic. What image does she use?",
      "audio": "audio/b2.2/unit-02-taste-figures/listen-1.mp3",
      "transcript": "La tarte au citron est une merveille : une pâte croustillante, une crème à peine acide — un petit nuage.",
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "a",
          "text": "The lemon tart is 'a little cloud' — crispy pastry, slightly tart cream"
        },
        {
          "id": "b",
          "text": "The tart is heavy as a stone and too sweet"
        },
        {
          "id": "c",
          "text": "She refuses to taste the dessert"
        }
      ],
      "correct": [
        "a"
      ],
      "explanation": "« un petit nuage » — a metaphor crowning the praise."
    },
    {
      "id": "ex-rd-1",
      "type": "read",
      "skill": "reading",
      "prompt": "Read this Proust-style memory and answer both questions.",
      "passageFr": "Le premier croissant de la boulangerie Garnier était une fête. La pâte, dorée comme un matin d'été, croustillait puis fondait — et chaque bouchée évoquait les dimanches de mon enfance, quand mon grand-père m'attendait devant la vitrine. J'adore les croissants ; mais celui-là n'était pas un croissant. C'était une madeleine de Proust.",
      "passageEn": "The first croissant from the Garnier bakery was a celebration. The pastry, golden like a summer morning, crackled then melted — and every bite evoked the Sundays of my childhood, when my grandfather waited for me by the window. I love croissants; but that one wasn't a croissant. It was a Proustian madeleine.",
      "questions": [
        {
          "id": "q1",
          "prompt": "« Dorée comme un matin d'été » is…",
          "options": [
            {
              "id": "a",
              "text": "a comparison (simile)"
            },
            {
              "id": "b",
              "text": "a metaphor"
            },
            {
              "id": "c",
              "text": "a negation"
            }
          ],
          "correct": [
            "a"
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "q2",
          "prompt": "What did each bite evoke?",
          "options": [
            {
              "id": "a",
              "text": "Childhood Sundays with his grandfather"
            },
            {
              "id": "b",
              "text": "His first day of school"
            },
            {
              "id": "c",
              "text": "A trip to the seaside"
            }
          ],
          "correct": [
            "a"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "ex-mc-4",
